WEBVTT

00:01.026 --> 00:04.026
Are you here to pick a Prime
Minister? Or deal with your son?

00:07.060 --> 00:09.676
Did you take care of that
situation with your mother?

00:09.700 --> 00:12.116
Tell your father.
I refuse.

00:12.140 --> 00:13.236
I can't...

00:13.260 --> 00:15.436
You're not aware of who
I was previously married to?

00:15.460 --> 00:16.636
No money? No lies?

00:16.660 --> 00:17.876
What's left?

00:17.900 --> 00:19.396
The truth. Can she win?

00:19.420 --> 00:21.116
She'd need all our support.

00:21.140 --> 00:22.516
I took the story to Caden.

00:22.540 --> 00:23.956
You know what he says?

00:23.980 --> 00:25.676
It was a robbery gone wrong.

00:25.700 --> 00:28.700
Don't tell me
what you think I want to hear.

00:28.940 --> 00:30.516
You can't do it, can you?

00:30.540 --> 00:33.540
Why do you make it so hard?

